// CHECK: Test persis_colmajor_sm86 Passed
// CHECK: Test persis_swizzle_sm86 Passed
// CHECK: Test persis_hilbert_sm86 Passed
// CHECK: Test persis_sta_sm90 Passed
// CHECK: Test persis_colmajor_sm90 Passed
// CHECK: Test persis_swizzle_sm90 Passed
// CHECK: Test persis_hilbert_sm90 Passed
// CHECK: Test persis_1p3c_sm90 Passed
// CHECK: All Tests Passed
